    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great project for someone willing to put in a little work. While it remains functional, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some fading paint on the roof. The interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, it is reliable for daily driving but will soon require routine suspension work and a brake service to bring it back to peak performance. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that needs some TLC.",
